OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNigeria declares state of  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Femergency over food        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Nigeria's President Bola Tinubu has    
OL,6, declared a state of emergency to tackle
OL,7, rising food prices and shortages.      
OL,9,FSome of the initiatives include using  
OL,10,Fmoney saved by the recent removal of a 
OL,11,Ffuel subsidy to provide fertiliser and 
OL,12,Fgrain to farmers.                      
OL,14,FProtection is also to be increased for 
OL,15,Ffarmers, many of whom have abandoned   
OL,16,Ftheir land after becoming the target of
OL,17,Fgangs that kidnap for ransom.          
OL,19,FPoorer households are to be helped too 
OL,20,Fwith $10 (#8) a month for six months.  
